{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Clean house again in this all-new <i>Punch-Out!!</i>-inspired Knockout adventure! Embark on this journey across the nation\u2014and the world\u2014as one of the newest rookie agents of the Federal Boxing Investigations (FBI) Bureau. In a world thrown into disarray, with nearly everything decided through boxing, will you rise to the occasion and face off against some of the most villainous characters? The dreaded Scam Brawler\u2019s jabs or the sharp claws of the Crazy Cat Lady could end your career before it truly starts. Can you solve these challenging global crises, or is the world destined to crumble into chaos?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The World of Knockout</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Knockout 2 pits you against the worst of society and the only way out is with your fists. Someone cut in line at the grocery store? That's a boxing match. Offended a scam caller? That's a boxing match, too. In fact, all laws, court cases, and skimping out on sandwich toppings are resolved through combat in a world where civil discourse has failed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Best Black Suits</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock new gear to customize your boxer and save the world! Each opponent is a puzzle to be picked apart. From Karens to Bridezillas, learn each opponent\u2019s fighting style and expertly clap back, perfect-blocking and countering your way to direct each match like a symphony conductor. The road to victory might not be easy, but it <i>will</i> be hilarious.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Classic arcade boxing action with tight timing and even tighter controls in the style of <i>Punch-Out!!</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A wild journey across the globe solving everyone's problems. With your fists.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A single-player story every bit as comedically scathing as the first game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fully customizable boxer with unlockable gear.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Extra challenges with Steam Achievements for each character.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Refined core game mechanics building upon the risk and reward boxing style of the first game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Full keyboard and gamepad support.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete in-game tutorial to teach you the boxing basics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At least one duck.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Wishlist the game today and prepare to save the world, one punch at a time!</h2>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349350/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729528020","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349350/page.bg.jpg?t=1729528020","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349350/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729528020","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349350/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1729528020","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Stats","id":15}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Clean house again in this all-new <i>Punch-Out!!</i>-inspired Knockout adventure! Embark on this journey across the nation\u2014and the world\u2014as one of the newest rookie agents of the Federal Boxing Investigations (FBI) Bureau. In a world thrown into disarray, with nearly everything decided through boxing, will you rise to the occasion and face off against some of the most villainous characters? The dreaded Scam Brawler\u2019s jabs or the sharp claws of 